JUMA-Sidewinder + remix's by  DublinXpressRecordings

&nbsp;
Artist: Juma Label: Dublin Xpress Recordings Release name: SidewinderFile under: Minimal/ Minimal Release date: 23-02-2010 Press release: Juma is Owen Johnston, one of Northern Ireland's leading new DJs and Producers. Inspired by people like Jean Michele Jarre, Kraftwerk, Michael Jackson, Ferry Corsten, Paul Van Dyk and Ulster's own X-Ray, Owen has been developing his sound that encompass Trance, Progressive and Minimal. Like other DXR artists Brian Taaffe Owen Johnston fuses Minimal and Trance with aplomb and dare we claim credit but creates Nu Minimal Trance. Sidewinder is a deep, dark track from Owen aka Juma and shows off his studio skills and dance floor acumen, however, the remixes are simply irresistible. The Photosonic Orchestra and Nachklangmusik offer two of the best tunes ever on DXR and DXR's very own JR drops a bobshell of an abstract almost beatless version that all adds up to 4 cracking track release.Track: 1 - Juma - Sidewinder (The Photosonic Orchestra's Intense Mix) Track: 2 - Juma - Sidewinder (Nachklangmusik's Remix) Track: 3 - Juma - Sidewinder (Jay Riordan's Beatless in Ballymun Mix) Track: 4 - Juma - Sidewinder (Original) Catalogue Code: DXR049 Barcode: 8717578194940
